      • createResolver

        public static GroupResolver createResolver()
        Setups a GroupResolver by searching for supported plugins on the server. Vault will always take preference over other supported plugins for obvious reasons.

        This method will never return null, but default to a SuperPermsResolver instead.

        Returns:
        the created GroupResolver
